# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:29
translate spanish hwb_s12d_a719d43d:

    # "We wander around for a while until we find another viewpoint that's empty of other people. I’m guessing that a lot of the treasure hunters are out looking now, since the oppressive heat isn’t as bad."
    "Vagamos un rato hasta que encontramos otro mirador que está vacío de gente. Supongo que muchos de los cazadores de tesoros ya están buscando, ya que el calor opresivo no es tan intenso."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:31
translate spanish hwb_s12d_9e00518c:

    # "I lean against the rail, my head propped up on my arms. The cool metal feels nice against my skin. Marina does the same. She sighs wistfully."
    "Me apoyo contra la barandilla, con la cabeza apoyada en mis brazos. El metal frío se siente agradable contra mi piel. Marina hace lo mismo. Suspira con nostalgia."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:38
translate spanish hwb_s12d_16c6a3f4:

    # Marina "So pretty…"
    Marina "Так красиво…"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:40
translate spanish hwb_s12d_f51537cf:

    # Amber "Which part?"
    Amber "Что именно?"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:44
translate spanish hwb_s12d_f8e351a8:

    # Marina "All of it! Especially the sunset."
    Marina "Да все вокруг! Особенно закат."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:46
translate spanish hwb_s12d_40e9351f:

    # "Nearly all the sunlight has been swallowed by the canyon’s colossal darkness. Shadows cast by the stones mute the gorgeous colors as the sun melts into the tip of the canyon."
    "Casi toda la luz del sol ha sido devorada por la oscuridad colosal del cañón. Las sombras proyectadas por las piedras apagan los colores hermosos mientras el sol se derrite en la punta del cañón."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:48
translate spanish hwb_s12d_80524398:

    # "It’s barren and desolate, but Marina’s right—it’s pretty."
    "Es árido y desolado, pero Marina tiene razón: es bonito."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:52
translate spanish hwb_s12d_0a0c2d1c:

    # Marina "Oh! Let’s take a picture! Before it gets too dark!"
    Marina "О! Давай сфотографируемся! Пока не слишком стемнело!"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:57
translate spanish hwb_s12d_139dc9cf:

    # Amber "Uhh…."
    Amber "Ммм…."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:61
translate spanish hwb_s12d_d05c3393:

    # Marina "You’re not getting out of this one! You haven’t been in any of the pictures today."
    Marina "Тебе не избежать этого! К тому же, тебя не было ни на одной фотографии за сегодня."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:65
translate spanish hwb_s12d_072bf633:

    # Amber "Yeah, that’s on purpose."
    Amber "Да, и это было намеренно."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:67
translate spanish hwb_s12d_9d7c75cc:

    # Marina "Scooch in."
    Marina "Кучкуемся."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:71
translate spanish hwb_s12d_e4f9150e:

    # Amber "Like, together?"
    Amber "Типо, рядом друг с другом?"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:75
translate spanish hwb_s12d_62c42327:

    # Marina "Duh!"
    Marina "Пф!"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:85
translate spanish hwb_s12d_91ddb9ba:

    # "She slides towards me, and I squirm away on instinct."
    "Se desliza hacia mí, y yo me aparto por instinto."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:89
translate spanish hwb_s12d_55fac5ba:

    # Marina "What’s wrong?"
    Marina "Что-то не так?"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:93
translate spanish hwb_s12d_2d428faf:

    # "Immediately, before I can answer, she grins slyly."
    "Inmediatamente, antes de que pueda responder, sonríe con picardía."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:95
translate spanish hwb_s12d_a50079bd:

    # Marina "W{cps=4}aaaaaaaaaaait{/cps} a second."
    Marina "Погоди-ка{cps=4}аааааа{/cps} секунду."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:99
translate spanish hwb_s12d_cee763c5:

    # Marina "You’re camera-shy, aren’t you?"
    Marina "Ты у нас стесняешься камеры, не так ли?"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:103
translate spanish hwb_s12d_cb3df833:

    # Amber "Am not!"
    Amber "Неправда!"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:105
translate spanish hwb_s12d_1986e1f1:

    # "I retort a little too quickly."
    "Respondo un poco demasiado rápido."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:109
translate spanish hwb_s12d_b9b8ad13:

    # Marina "Oh?"
    Marina "Оу?"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:111
translate spanish hwb_s12d_dc914371:

    # "Clearly, she doesn’t believe me."
    "Claramente, no me cree."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:115
translate spanish hwb_s12d_04a6c096:

    # Amber "It’s not that I’m afraid of them or anything, I just don’t like having my picture taken."
    Amber "Не то чтобы я боюсь камер или что-то в этом роде, я просто не люблю, когда меня фотографируют."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:119
translate spanish hwb_s12d_d2b59640:

    # Marina "How come?"
    Marina "Как же так?"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:123
translate spanish hwb_s12d_8619f2c6:

    # "I shrug."
    "Me encojo de hombros."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:125
translate spanish hwb_s12d_19818ac6:

    # Amber "Just don’t."
    Amber "Просто не люблю и все."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:129
translate spanish hwb_s12d_8aba3a6d:

    # Marina "Well, you’ll have to deal with it this time!"
    Marina "Но в этот раз тебе придется иметь дело со мной!"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:136
translate spanish hwb_s12d_7708db18:

    # "She zips over and, before I can react, has pressed her cheek to mine."
    "Se acerca volando y, antes de que pueda reaccionar, ha presionado su mejilla contra la mía."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:144
translate spanish hwb_s12d_3e5e83e7:

    # "The shutter clicks and I’m momentarily stunned by the flash."
    "El obturador hace clic y quedo momentáneamente aturdido por el destello."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:149
translate spanish hwb_s12d_05b66a5d:

    # "Before I can protest or enjoy the closeness, she’s already pulled away and is checking the results."
    "Antes de que pueda protestar o disfrutar de la cercanía, ya se ha apartado y está revisando los resultados."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:153
translate spanish hwb_s12d_5854a21d:

    # Marina "It’s cute! Look!"
    Marina "Как мило! Ты глянь!"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:155
translate spanish hwb_s12d_b3eb3580:

    # "She shoves the camera into my face, but it’s so close and the screen is so small that I can’t actually see the picture."
    "Me mete la cámara en la cara, pero está tan cerca y la pantalla es tan pequeña que no puedo ver la foto."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:159
translate spanish hwb_s12d_c7f36f36:

    # "I just nod."
    "Solo asiento."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:161
translate spanish hwb_s12d_7a8fee96:

    # Marina "I can’t wait to get these developed!"
    Marina "Не могу дождаться, когда их проявят!"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:163
translate spanish hwb_s12d_6467a83e:

    # "Turning to me, Marina pauses."
    "Volviéndose hacia mí, Marina se detiene."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:167
translate spanish hwb_s12d_5669ce9c:

    # Marina "How do you get photos developed, anyway?"
    Marina "Кстати, а что нужно, чтобы проявить фотографии?"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:171
translate spanish hwb_s12d_26af731d:

    # Amber "We’ll have to take them to a store and have them do it. Most big supermarkets can."
    Amber "Мы отнесем их в специальный отдел в магазине, и там это сделают. Он есть в большинстве крупных супермаркетов."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:175
translate spanish hwb_s12d_7cce4ffd:

    # Marina "Okay! First thing tomorrow then!"
    Marina "Хорошо!  Будет первым делом на завтра!"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:179
translate spanish hwb_s12d_fb39b1c5:

    # Amber "Sure."
    Amber "Разумеется."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:184
translate spanish hwb_s12d_60168809:

    # "Like a hummingbird, Marina darts forward and gives me a tight hug."
    "Como un colibrí, Marina se lanza hacia adelante y me da un abrazo apretado."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:188
translate spanish hwb_s12d_d39148bd:

    # Marina "Thanks for coming out here. It’s been so amazing. I hope it was worth it."
    Marina "Спасибо, что привела меня сюда. Это было чудесно. Надеюсь, и для тебя это того стоило."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:190
translate spanish hwb_s12d_d54c460e:

    # "I look down at her, pressed against me."
    "La miro hacia abajo, presionada contra mí."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:192
translate spanish hwb_s12d_6be53160:

    # Amber "Yeah, it was."
    Amber "Да,конечно."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:199
translate spanish hwb_s12d_72ee47c1:

    # "Marina pulls away, to my great disappointment. She opens her mouth like she’s going to say something, but then seems to change her mind."
    "Marina se aparta, para mi gran decepción. Abre la boca como si fuera a decir algo, pero luego parece cambiar de opinión."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:203
translate spanish hwb_s12d_5f1d9671:

    # Amber "What?"
    Amber "Что?"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:207
translate spanish hwb_s12d_02eb456c:

    # Marina "What what?"
    Marina "Что «что»?"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:209
translate spanish hwb_s12d_4e587cad:

    # Amber "You were about to say something. What was it?"
    Amber "Ты собиралась сказать что-то . Что же?"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:213
translate spanish hwb_s12d_51f4d410:

    # Marina "Oh, uh… Never mind."
    Marina "Оу, эээ … Неважно."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:217
translate spanish hwb_s12d_51098c05:

    # Amber "Hey, you can’t do that. Now I really wanna know!"
    Amber "Эй, так не пойдет. Я действительно хочу знать!"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:221
translate spanish hwb_s12d_13e3eb97:

    # "She giggles, but it’s distracted-sounding."
    "Se ríe, pero suena distraída."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:225
translate spanish hwb_s12d_58d53a6d:

    # Marina "Okay, fine."
    Marina "Ладно, хорошо."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:229
translate spanish hwb_s12d_3080ea4e:

    # Marina "I was just gonna ask, why is it that you hate Mariah and her group so much?"
    Marina "Я просто хотела спросить, почему ты так ненавидишь Марию и ее спутников?"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:233
translate spanish hwb_s12d_aa668a0b:

    # Amber "Where’d that come from?"
    Amber "С чего ты это взяла?"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:237
translate spanish hwb_s12d_d018628e:

    # "Marina turns away and stares out over the canyon again. It’s getting pretty dark. She’s quiet for a moment before she talks."
    "Marina se da la vuelta y vuelve a mirar el cañón. Está bastante oscuro. Se queda en silencio un momento antes de hablar."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:241
translate spanish hwb_s12d_167e11fb:

    # Marina "I dunno. You just complain about them a lot."
    Marina "Не знаю. Просто ты постоянно жалуешься на них."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:245
translate spanish hwb_s12d_9b901199:

    # Amber "I don’t hate them, dummy."
    Amber "Я не ненавижу их, глупенькая."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:247
translate spanish hwb_s12d_175342e0:

    # Amber "Joe and Tess are fine. It’s just Mariah I have a problem with."
    Amber "Джо и Тесс нормальные. Просто у меня есть некоторые проблемы с Марией."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:249
translate spanish hwb_s12d_d2b59640_1:

    # Marina "How come?"
    Marina "Отчего же?"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:253
translate spanish hwb_s12d_6a685b29:

    # Amber "She’s a bitch. Loud and rude and obnoxious. I really hate people like that."
    Amber "Она сука. Громкая, грубая и наглая. Я терпеть не могу таких людей."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:257
translate spanish hwb_s12d_1879fc3c:

    # Amber "She thinks she’s always right, too."
    Amber "А еще она считает, что она всегда права."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:261
translate spanish hwb_s12d_29dcad6a:

    # Marina "Sounds like someone else I know."
    Marina "Похоже на кое-кого еще, кого я знаю."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:265
translate spanish hwb_s12d_79e7a31b:

    # Amber "Don’t give me that! We’re nothing alike!"
    Amber "Не говори так! У нас нет ничего общего с ней!"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:269
translate spanish hwb_s12d_063017ff:

    # "Marina laughs."
    "Marina se ríe."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:273
translate spanish hwb_s12d_ae91499a:

    # Marina "Yeah, yeah."
    Marina "Да-да."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:279
translate spanish hwb_s12d_450c6482:

    # "Half a minute passes in silence."
    "Pasa medio minuto en silencio."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:283
translate spanish hwb_s12d_083b7721:

    # Marina "You’re way cuter than she is."
    Marina "Ты намного милее, чем она."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:287
translate spanish hwb_s12d_0825cf7a:

    # "Time stops, and so does my heart."
    "El tiempo se detiene, y también mi corazón."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:291
translate spanish hwb_s12d_1a50f06b:

    # "Everything feels like it’s frozen."
    "Todo se siente como si estuviera congelado."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:293
translate spanish hwb_s12d_cc4bb842:

    # "I look over at Marina, but she’s looking at the canyon, not me."
    "Miro hacia Marina, pero ella está viendo el cañón, no a mí."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:295
translate spanish hwb_s12d_c7076cae:

    # "Still just a couple inches away."
    "Todavía a solo un par de centímetros de distancia."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:297
translate spanish hwb_s12d_df59c98f:

    # "I gulp, swallowing the lump forming in my throat."
    "Trago saliva, tragándome el nudo que se forma en mi garganta."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:301
translate spanish hwb_s12d_c616256a:

    # Amber "You said that before, I think. You’re cuter."
    Amber "Ты уже говорила это, кажется. Ты милее."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:305
translate spanish hwb_s12d_9e6cafec:

    # Marina "Oh hush! I’m trying to compliment you."
    Marina "Ой, цыц! Я пытаюсь сделать тебе комплимент."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:309
translate spanish hwb_s12d_e8fe642a:

    # "I fall silent for a moment, not sure of how to respond."
    "Me quedo en silencio por un momento, sin saber cómo responder."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:313
translate spanish hwb_s12d_4167c007:

    # Amber "You know, back when we first met, I meant what I said about you being cute, too."
    Amber "Знаешь, когда мы впервые встретились, тогда я тоже на полном серьезе сказала, что ты милая."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:317
translate spanish hwb_s12d_5b24fe21:

    # "She giggles again."
    "Ella vuelve a reírse."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:319
translate spanish hwb_s12d_31068672:

    # Marina "I’d forgotten about that."
    Marina "Я уже не помню этого."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:321
translate spanish hwb_s12d_73905705:

    # "As if on cue, a light breeze starts up, causing her hair to billow out like a cloud. Her sidetail, hastily bound, looks as if it might come undone."
    "Como si fuera una señal, comienza una brisa ligera, haciendo que su cabello se agite como una nube. Su cola de caballo lateral, atada apresuradamente, parece que podría deshacerse."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:325
translate spanish hwb_s12d_8a711b95:

    # "Finally, she turns to look at me, her eyes wide and lips glistening."
    "Finalmente, se gira para mirarme, con los ojos muy abiertos y los labios brillantes."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:327
translate spanish hwb_s12d_3b20882b:

    # "My palms are dry and my knees tremble."
    "Tengo las palmas secas y las rodillas me tiemblan."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:332
translate spanish hwb_s12d_7498d042:

    # "Gulping yet again, I cross the short distance between us in a half-step, leaning in and-"
    "Tragando de nuevo, cruzo la corta distancia entre nosotras con medio paso, inclinándome y..."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:336
translate spanish hwb_s12d_4006c928:

    # Mariah "There you are!"
    Mariah "Вот вы где!"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:338
translate spanish hwb_s12d_e12e1f0c:

    # "Someone’s about to die."
    "Alguien está a punto de morir."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:340
translate spanish hwb_s12d_fc8ed33a:

    # "Mariah’s shrill voice cuts through the moment, rupturing my eardrums and patience. I pull away, and Marina has already turned around to face them."
    "La voz estridente de Mariah atraviesa el momento, rompiéndome los tímpanos y la paciencia. Me aparto, y Marina ya se ha girado para enfrentarlas."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:367
translate spanish hwb_s12d_bf82576a:

    # "The trio appear like specters out of the darkness."
    "El trío aparece como espectros desde la oscuridad."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:369
translate spanish hwb_s12d_22a5a2f9:

    # Mariah "You left us behind!"
    Mariah "Вы бросили нас!"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:373
translate spanish hwb_s12d_78d40ec1:

    # Amber "We tried to, at least."
    Amber "Ну... пытались."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:375
translate spanish hwb_s12d_10c816b4:

    # Mariah "You were the ones who dragged us out here. I at least expected you to stick around."
    Mariah "Это вы затащили нас сюда. По крайней мере, я ожидала, что вы будете держаться рядом."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:377
translate spanish hwb_s12d_fe548f72:

    # "Cowed into submission, Marina’s shoulders fall."
    "Acobardada, los hombros de Marina se hunden."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:381
translate spanish hwb_s12d_04232613:

    # Amber "Back off. I wanted to go see the sunset without you sighing about it."
    Amber "Отвянь. Я только лишь хотел взглянуть на закат без твоего причитания на фоне."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:383
translate spanish hwb_s12d_f10bcd3f:

    # Mariah "Whatever. It was a waste of time either way."
    Mariah "Какая разница. Это в любом случае пустая трата времени."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:385
translate spanish hwb_s12d_a240de45:

    # Mariah "Come on, we’re going back."
    Mariah "Пошли, мы возвращаемся обратно."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:398
translate spanish hwb_s12d_7601ee55:

    # "Mariah lopes off down the path at a brisk pace. Marina and Tess are back to photographing anything and everything, though the low light means that the pictures won’t show up."
    "Mariah se aleja por el sendero a paso rápido. Marina y Tess vuelven a fotografiar todo lo que ven, aunque la poca luz significa que las fotos no saldrán."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:400
translate spanish hwb_s12d_c9803d2c:

    # "Joseph and I trail behind at the end of the party."
    "Joseph y yo vamos detrás, al final del grupo."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:404
translate spanish hwb_s12d_6f512a35:

    # Joseph "How was the sunset?"
    Joseph "Как закат?"

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:408
translate spanish hwb_s12d_f4e22206:

    # "Sighing, I pull ahead. Right now, even Joseph seems like a little too much."
    "Suspirando, me adelanto. Ahora mismo, incluso Joseph parece demasiado."

# game/script/hwb_s12d.rpy:412
translate spanish hwb_s12d_84ed7397:

    # Amber "It was okay."
    Amber "Неплох."

translate spanish strings:

    # script/hwb_s12d.rpy:29
    old "Avoiding the trio"
    new "Avoiding the trio"

